"perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151283}, {"id": 264225, "content": "微信收到领导问：在吗？  回复：在的。  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398021}, {"id": 240931, "content": "朋友非常热心的开始“世纪佳缘”式现场牵线活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609486}, {"id": 240932, "content": "玩狼人杀的时候，六个人，只剩我一匹狼", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119358}, {"id": 240933, "content": "oh no", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143756}, {"id": 241445, "content": "喝酒。\n喝完白酒，有人提议喝啤酒，大家都说来来来………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046034}, {"id": 240934, "content": "和现任逛街遇到前任.....   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177090}, {"id": 240936, "content": "上台发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100998}, {"id": 245032, "content": "吃完饭后干嘛啊？\n\n哈哈，去k吧啦\n\n我心中：天啦，我不行了，我要装出要生病的模样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170095}, {"id": 242218, "content": "分手之后才知道对象和闺蜜有一腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157633}, {"id": 240939, "content": "等车的时候被人搭话闲聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151336}, {"id": 241202, "content": "单身，和异性朋友出门玩耍，他要合照发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125979}, {"id": 240949, "content": "上课老师要强行互动\n点人回答问题时", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959901}, {"id": 241205, "content": "上课点人回答问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133021}, {"id": 240950, "content": "打球前，随口一句，去么，心里念叨你千万别去啊！(对方属于只许他动你，不能你粘他一根汗毛)", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144479}, {"id": 240952, "content": "当别了聊我的黑历史时 我装作无所谓╮(╯_╰)╭ 内心是抓狂的 表面笑嘻嘻 内心mmp ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060839}, {"id": 241465, "content": "现一策划，好多年前做过一两年设计，我做6年，跟TA合作总要挑设计毛病，还直要源件说自己改，此时我只能来句：你看着办吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082506}, {"id": 240954, "content": "生日请吃饭刚好四个人，其中一个女生说我能不能带我男朋友（很久没有吃顿好的）", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132746}, {"id": 242490, "content": "赌一把", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158806}, {"id": 240955, "content": "回老公老家搭他前女友的顺风车算不算", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 241213, "content": "大学的选修课教室里无聊ex.:-)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152591}, {"id": 240959, "content": "领导撺的局大家都在尬聊，还要加场。我猜他特别享受众星捧月的feel", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151388}, {"id": 240960, "content": "狼人杀当自己是狼人时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102915}, {"id": 243264, "content": "朋友结婚请吃火锅，让我点荤菜说：不要牛羊一类的肉、不要辣就好了… 您老还是去黄焖鸡吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993110}, {"id": 240962, "content": "大家开始聊各自男朋友。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722549}, {"id": 241219, "content": "领导一本正经宣布一件“大事儿”的时候！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092499}, {"id": 240964, "content": "好好爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112307}, {"id": 240965, "content": "宠你，你还要怎样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150156}, {"id": 243526, "content": "说到底就是碰上奇葩人干的奇葩事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098434}, {"id": 241223, "content": "这节副科上主科儿吧……众学生举手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136030}, {"id": 241224, "content": "好的我的女友粉是我的错我一个男的你们那么爱我我怎么可以公开谈恋爱呢我应该是被包养啊", "image": "img/option/option/20171011215816TeOsmCz0UIfSKHdW", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152648}, {"id": 241993, "content": "开会点名发言，上课点名回答问题，年会点名表演节目，等等点名行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 242762, "content": "其实我很生气，但我忍着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140954}, {"id": 240973, "content": "看似稳如老狗，实则慌的一笔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044090}, {"id": 240974, "content": "难得逃一次课 然后点名了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125060}, {"id": 240975, "content": "你要是真有需要，我这有些钱给你应急", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820255}, {"id": 241231, "content": "逢年过节亲戚来了，顺便带来他们的倒霉孩子，装作并不讨厌他们的样子，听着他们下次还要来还要点头说好啊好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131466}, {"id": 240976, "content": "房价高涨的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151479}]}